@startuml seq_24_approve_reject_post
title Sequence Diagram: UC-24 Approve / Reject Post

actor Moderator
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Moderation Controller" as Controller
participant "Moderation Service" as Service
participant "Post Repo" as Repo
participant "Event Bus\n(Go Channels)" as EventBus

Moderator -> Frontend: Open moderation queue
Frontend -> Controller: GET /api/moderation/queue
Controller -> Service: Get Pending Posts
Service -> Repo: Fetch posts with 'pending' status
Repo --> Service: List of pending posts
Service --> Controller: Pending posts data
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> Moderator: Display pending posts

Moderator -> Frontend: Review post & Click Approve or Reject
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/moderation/posts/{id}/decide {action, reason}
Controller -> Service: Process Moderation Decision
Service -> Repo: Verify moderator permissions
Repo --> Service: Permissions valid

alt Action is Approve
    Service -> Repo: Update post status to 'published'
    Repo --> Service: Status updated
else Action is Reject
    Service -> Repo: Update post status to 'rejected' & store reason
    Repo --> Service: Status updated
end

Service -> EventBus: Publish ModerationDecisionEvent
note right of EventBus
  Background goroutine notifies
  the post author
end note

Service --> Controller: Success
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> Moderator: Remove post from queue UI
@enduml